title: Coinbase on Grayscale Ethereum Spot ETF Application: “ETH Is a Commodity, Not a Security”
description: Coinbase has answered the SEC request for comments on the proposed rule change to list the ETH Grayscale Fund as a spot ETF. Coinbase stated that ether was a commodity, and its status has been publicly recognized in a variety of circumstances by U.S. agencies and courts.
